quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  41,1,Ha Mim
  41,2,"A revelation from the All-Merciful, the Most Merciful"
  41,3,A Book whose verses have been demarcated for people who know as an Arabic Qur´an
  41,4,bringing good news and giving warning; but most of them have turned away and do not hear
  41,5,"They say, ´Our hearts are covered up against what you call us to and there is a heaviness in our ears. There is a screen between us and you. So act — we are certainly acting.´"
  41,6,"Say: ´I am only a human being like yourselves. It is revealed to me that your god is One God. So be straight with Him and ask His forgiveness.´ Woe to those who associate others with Him"
  41,7,those who do not pay zakat and reject the Next World
  41,8,Those who have iman and do right actions will have a wage which never fails